OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780563951
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with murder
OL,4,Cof Ellis Cox
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in connection
OL,7,Fwith the murder of Ellis Cox nearly
OL,8,Ftwo years ago.
OL,10,FEllis was just 19 years old when he
OL,11,Fwas shot dead on Sunday, 23 June 2024,
OL,12,Fat the Liver Industrial Estate in
OL,13,FAintree, Liverpool, while cycling home.
OL,15,FMerseyside Police say a 24-year-old
OL,16,Fman from Walton, has been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,18,Fmurder and has been taken into custody
OL,19,Fto be questioned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
