FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780563951
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with murder
OL,4,Cof Ellis Cox
OL,6,FHe is the eighth person to be arrested
OL,7,Fin connection with this case, with all
OL,8,Fpeople previously arrested on
OL,9,Fconditional bail pending further
OL,10,Finquiries.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Steve Wilkinson
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our investigation continues to
OL,14,Fprogress and this man will be
OL,15,Fquestioned about Ellis' murder.
OL,17,F"Although we have made this arrest, I
OL,18,Fwant to urge anyone with information
OL,19,Fto come forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
