PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1780563951
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with murder
OL,4,Cof Ellis Cox
OL,6,F"I want to thank the community so far
OL,7,Ffor the information they have provided
OL,8,Fto us and please be assured that we
OL,9,Fare determined to get justice for
OL,10,FEllis' family."
OL,12,FMerseyside Police are urging anyone
OL,13,Fwith information, mobile phone
OL,14,Ffootage, or dashcam recordings to come
OL,15,Fforward.
